channel.title: Anyone play these games?
channel.description:
If you play any of these games, you can get free points in the link in my signature. Do surveys and stuff for points. That's not the only reason why I made this post, it's because you can get an iPod Shuffle, xBox360, etc...
Don't ask why I made this post... *asks* Fine, I want points... Don't ask why I want points... *asks* Don't know, I just want over 5000 points in case I ever end up playing those games O_o
Have fun!
